避開高峰時間。當局指，出城人士不可屬於被要求隔離的人士，而且須身體健康，沒有發燒、乾咳、氣喘等症狀，而出城人士到達目的地後，須做好不少過14天的健康監測，並向當地疫情防控指揮部門備案。<br />\n<br />\n至於滯留在外地的武漢市民及車輛，以及因保障疫情防控、城市運行、生產生活、防疫物資運輸等原因必須進城的人士和車輛，按省、市疫情防控指揮部有關規定辦理相關手續後，可以進城。當局在進出城通道設置站點，對出入的車輛和人員，進行檢查，包括核對身份、車輛消毒、體溫檢測、隔離救治、人員防護等工作。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266530&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1266530%26csid%3D261_341&d=SulGM1C%2FSMvfI9hDp2hpAr7WCVQ3d6ncBxZnFa%2FO6Ec%3D&h=931b2a7d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1266530&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"c8534e9eae0b81b91aa9a7ac144490b1d91b4cd4","tid":1894553,"uid":160094,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:18:36.000Z","msg":"腥香港人先會個喺&quot;可防可控&quot;時期去湖北過年<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76281a0cf0f0a4a0a563d0b7c9acc8281c0d0729","tid":1894553,"uid":30115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:19:27.000Z","msg":"有事就識反黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f381d5f024681be10f87f61307235697fbaa9bd","tid":1894553,"uid":119232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:19:39.000Z","msg":"呢啲真撚屌<br />\n倒共產黨米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50b6a7ad0bb02c4e5bebc0cf4e8f55afb8cfeca","tid":1894553,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e950f773139ea0f2666ac84d1c82ba13d3f792de","tid":1894553,"uid":152476,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"f273d99d0bcd74f81c39d09895bf41119cf28769","tid":1894553,"uid":25560,"like":107,"dislike":0,"score":107,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:14:20.000Z","msg":"我懷疑好多係有香港身分證的大陸人"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:16:25.000Z","msg":"個心仲係中國人，但拎住香港身份證攞著數"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-24T04:20:36.000Z","msg":"中國人無論咩國籍都係中國人<img sr